column2: SELECT     T.ID, T.SpecObjID, S.bestObjID as photoObjID, T.hostra, T.hostdec, S.ra as SDSSra, S.dec as SDSSdec, S.z as SDSSredshift, P.petroMag_u, P.petroMag_g, P.petroMag_r, P.petroMag_i, P.petroMag_z, P.petroMagErr_u, P.petroMagErr_g, P.petroMagErr_r, P.petroMagErr_i, P.petroMagErr_z, P.extinction_u, P.extinction_g, P.extinction_r, P.extinction_i, P.extinction_z INTO     mydb.SpecObj_petroMags_compare FROM     DR1#.SpecObj as S, DR1#.PhotoObj as P, mydb.compareSpec_ObjID as T WHERE     S.specObjID = T.SpecObjID
